  "page": "A Clash of Kings-Chapter 57",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background-color:rgb(239, 175, 51)\">Sansa V</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i> chapter</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_clash_of_kings\" title=\"A clash of kings\"><img alt=\"AClashOfKings.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/39/AClashOfKings.jpg/220px-AClashOfKings.jpg\" width=\"220\" height=\"362\" class=\"thumbborder\" srcset=\"/images/3/39/AClashOfKings.jpg 1.5x\" /></a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">POV</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Sansa Stark</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Red_Keep\" title=\"Red Keep\">Red Keep</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Page</th><td>\n593 <small>UK HC</small> <small>(<a href=\"/index.php/Chapters_Table_of_contents\" title=\"Chapters Table of contents\">Other versions</a>)</small></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:rgb(239, 175, 51)\">Chapter chronology <small>(<a href=\"/index.php/Chapters\" title=\"Chapters\">All</a>)</small></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_52\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 52\">Sansa IV</a><br />↑</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_56\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 56\">Theon V</a></td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">&#160;←</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle; padding-right:0.1em; padding-left:0.1em;\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sansa V</a></td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">→&#160;</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_58\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 58\">Davos III</a></td>\n</tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n↓<br /><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_60\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 60\">Sansa VI</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Synopsis\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Synopsis</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Character_List\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Character List</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Notes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References_and_Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References and Notes</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Synopsis\">Synopsis</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_57&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Synopsis\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Sansa</a> is in the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Keep\" title=\"Red Keep\">Red Keep</a>'s <a href=\"/index.php/Royal_sept\" title=\"Royal sept\">royal sept</a>. The <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Blackwater\" title=\"Battle of the Blackwater\">Battle of the Blackwater</a> is underway and the people in the sept are waiting for the outcome. \n</p><p><a href=\"/index.php/Joffrey_Baratheon\" title=\"Joffrey Baratheon\">Joffrey</a> obliged her to see him off before. He made her kiss <a href=\"/index.php/Hearteater\" title=\"Hearteater\">his sword</a> promising that he would kill <a href=\"/index.php/Stannis_Baratheon\" title=\"Stannis Baratheon\">Stannis</a> with it. Sansa hopes that Joffrey will fight himself and get himself killed. She told him that her brother <a href=\"/index.php/Robb_Stark\" title=\"Robb Stark\">Robb</a> was always in the thick of the fight. Joffrey replied that he will kill Robb as well. \n</p><p>In the sept the people are singing. Sansa sings with them until they start praying for the victory of Joffrey. Silently Sansa prays for his defeat and goes away. As she leaves for <a href=\"/index.php/Maegor%27s_Holdfast\" title=\"Maegor&#39;s Holdfast\">Maegor's Holdfast</a> she can hear the sound of battle. \n</p><p>Within the holdfast Sansa enters the Queen's Ballroom, where there is almost every highborn woman in the city, along with a handful of old men and young boys. Sansa notices <a href=\"/index.php/Ilyn_Payne\" title=\"Ilyn Payne\">Ilyn Payne</a>. When Sansa asks why Ilyn is present, Cersei states he would deal with treasonous guards and defend Cersei and Sansa if <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> is sacked.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;N 1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character_List\">Character List</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_57&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character List\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" width=\"100%\">\n\n<tbody><tr valign=\"top\">\n<td style=\"width:33%;\">\n<p><b>Appearing:</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Joffrey_Baratheon\" title=\"Joffrey Baratheon\">Joffrey Baratheon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Meryn_Trant\" title=\"Meryn Trant\">Meryn Trant</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Mandon_Moore\" title=\"Mandon Moore\">Mandon Moore</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Osmund_Kettleblack\" title=\"Osmund Kettleblack\">Osmund Kettleblack</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tanda_Stokeworth\" title=\"Tanda Stokeworth\">Tanda Stokeworth</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Falyse_Stokeworth\" title=\"Falyse Stokeworth\">Falyse Stokeworth</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lollys_Stokeworth\" title=\"Lollys Stokeworth\">Lollys Stokeworth</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Shae\" title=\"Shae\">Shae</a> (Lollys's maid)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Ilyn_Payne\" title=\"Ilyn Payne\">Ilyn Payne</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Osfryd_Kettleblack\" title=\"Osfryd Kettleblack\">Osfryd Kettleblack</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Cersei_Lannister\" title=\"Cersei Lannister\">Cersei Lannister</a></li></ul>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%;\">\n<p><b>Mentioned</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Tommen_Baratheon\" title=\"Tommen Baratheon\">Tommen Baratheon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Stannis_Baratheon\" title=\"Stannis Baratheon\">Stannis Baratheon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Robb_Stark\" title=\"Robb Stark\">Robb Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rickon_Stark\" title=\"Rickon Stark\">Rickon Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Bran_Stark\" title=\"Bran Stark\">Bran Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Stark\" title=\"Catelyn Stark\">Catelyn Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Hoster_Tully\" title=\"Hoster Tully\">Hoster Tully</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Edmure_Tully\" title=\"Edmure Tully\">Edmure Tully</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jeyne_Poole\" title=\"Jeyne Poole\">Jeyne Poole</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Robert_I_Baratheon\" title=\"Robert I Baratheon\">Robert I Baratheon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Mordane\" title=\"Mordane\">Mordane</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Dontos_Hollard\" title=\"Dontos Hollard\">Dontos Hollard</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jory_Cassel\" title=\"Jory Cassel\">Jory Cassel</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Luwin\" title=\"Luwin\">Luwin</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Sandor_Clegane\" title=\"Sandor Clegane\">Sandor Clegane</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Symeon_Star-Eyes\" title=\"Symeon Star-Eyes\">Symeon Star-Eyes</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Aemon_Targaryen_(son_of_Viserys_II)\" title=\"Aemon Targaryen (son of Viserys II)\">Aemon the Dragonknight</a></li></ul>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Notes\">Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_57&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Cersei has also tasked Ilyn with killing herself and Sansa if they are to be captured by Stannis's men.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References_and_Notes\">References and Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_57&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References and Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\" style=\"-webkit-column-width:200px; -moz-column-width:200px; column-width:200px; -webkit-column-count:2; -moz-column-count:2; column-count:2;\">\n</div>\n<ul><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://slynt.blogspot.com/2012/01/re-read-sansa-v-chapter-of-songs.html\">Analyses and summary of the chapter</a> in the course of a 10th reread by Slynt.</li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.tor.com/blogs/2012/07/a-read-of-ice-and-fire-a-clash-of-kings-part-28\">Review and summary</a> by Leigh Butler.</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403185107\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.085 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.317 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 275/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 1150/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 7749/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 894/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 387/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.220/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 5.37 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  290.760      1 -total\n 98.39%  286.067      1 Template:Infobox_Chapter_ACfK\n 98.05%  285.080      1 Template:Infobox_Chapter\n 97.69%  284.039      1 Template:Infobox\n  0.98%    2.848      1 Template:Notes\n  0.87%    2.534      2 Template:References\n  0.47%    1.373      2 Template:Work_color\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:4205-0!canonical and ti